Usage: unassignBump [-help] {-allBumps  | -byBumpName {list} | -byBumpSite {list} | -selected }

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-allBumps              # unassign all bumps (bool, optional)
-byBumpName {list}     # name of bumps to unassign (string, optional)
-byBumpSite {list}     # name of sites, bump of these site will be unassign
                       # (string, optional)
-selected              # unassign selected bumps (bool, optional)